<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٤٩) -<span class="c5"> العفر:</span> التراب.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٥٣) -<span class="c5"> الخرق:</span> الرايات.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٥٥) -<span class="c5"> شرح النهج:</span> وتصرعت.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>٥٦) -<span class="c5"> شرح النهج:</span> بجسومهم تفري،<span class="c5"> الخوامع:</span> الضباع.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>